strings.text: Your eyes are bigger than your stomach.
I'd give you a nasty look but you already got one.
If you're going to be two faced, at least make one of them pretty.
The only way you'll get laid is if you crawl up a chicken's ass and wait.
Scientists say the universe is made up of neutrons, protons, and electrons. When I met you, I discovered morons.
Why is it acceptable for you to be an idiot but not for me to point it out?
Which sexual position produces the ugliest children? Ask your mother.
Your doctor called with your colonoscopy results. Good news - they found your head.
You are proof that evolution can go in reverse.
The zoo called. They were wondering how you got out of your cage.
I was hoping for a battle of wits but you appear to be unarmed.
Jesus loves you... but everyone else thinks you're an asshole.
I thought of you today. It reminded me to take the garbage out.
If you were any saltier, you'd be a pack of Pringles.
You're so ugly when you look in the mirror, your reflection looks away.
Quick - check your face! I just found your nose in my business.
I may love to shop but I'm not buying your bull.
Gay? I'm straighter than the pole your mom dances on.
Repeat after me: Semen is *not* hair gel.
You are the most popular kid in home-school.
Shut up, you'll never be the man your mother is.
You're a failed abortion whose birth certificate is an apology from the condom factory.
You must have been born on a highway, because that's where most accidents happen.
You're so ugly Hello Kitty said goodbye to you.
Your mamma so fat she has to wear 2 watches because she covers two time zones.
You're probably that kid that climbed a glass wall to see what was on the other side.
Your life is like toilet paper, weak and shitty.
You've got the perfect face for a call center.
